# 👻 Phantom Clicker

A premium autoclicker with macro scripting, click recording, and global hotkeys.

## [⬇ Download Latest Version](https://github.com/IRuinedYou/PhantomClicker/releases/latest)

---

## Features

- ⚡ Autoclicker with fixed, random, or custom pattern intervals
- 🔴 Record & replay your clicks exactly
- 📜 Macro scripting — write or export recordings into editable scripts
- 🎯 Fixed position clicking with a screen picker
- 🧠 Humanization mode so clicks don't look robotic
- 🔥 Global hotkeys — fully customizable, works in any app
- 🔇 Minimize to tray, runs in background
- 📦 One installer, no .NET required, auto-updates built in

## Requirements

- Windows 10/11 (x64)
- That's it — the installer handles everything

## Safe & Clean

- Built with .NET 8 + WPF — uses official Windows APIs, not sketchy injection methods
- No obfuscation, no packed executables, no hidden processes
- Fully open source — the code is right here, see for yourself
- Windows Defender and antivirus won't flag it

## Installation

1. Download `PhantomClickerSetup.exe` from [Releases](https://github.com/IRuinedYou/PhantomClicker/releases/latest)
2. Run the installer
3. Launch from your desktop or Start Menu

The app checks for updates automatically on launch, or you can check manually in Settings.
